txt.en: 'You think it's strange to be talking to a cat? Well, I think it's strange to be talking to you, [placeholder]! Would you like to be flagged as having completed Volume II Book 8 of the Epic quest series? If so, speak to me again!
'Do I even need to tell you how this works? Oh well, just in case you weren't paying attention: completion of this quest will flag you as having completed Volume II Book 8 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character as having completed all the quests in Book 8 of the Epic quest series of Volume II.
Talk to Elevensies to complete Volume II, Book 8!
